<item>
            <title>[CXF-9168] No Micrometer Metric for requests failing schema validation on jax-ws endpoints</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-9168</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Setup:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Server side JAX-WS Endpoint with schema validation enabled&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;MetricsFeature enabled with a MicrometerMetricsProvider&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;When requests fail the schema validation, no metrics are updated on the MeterRegistry.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would be nice to be able to track schema validation failures through metrics, similarily to how other errors / faults can be tracked.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Attached is a failing unit test for this case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
